productname: GOLDEN HOUR Men’s Watch Fashion Sport Quartz Analog Mesh Stainless Steel Waterproof Chronograph Watches, Auto Date in Grey Hands, Color: Black
datereviewed: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews: This watch is pretty cool to have. How it looks is pretty amazing, but how it feels on your wrists . . . it's heavy and will have to get used to it. I have to admit when I first got this watch, adjusting the strap size to fit my wrist is more or less an incovience now. You just can;t adjust it as easily as all the other watches, nope! This watch gives you a tool to adjust it, and honestly: I wasn't really wowed by that. And also, this watch looks a bit too fancy for my day to day wear, but besides that: this watch is great for the price value!
